properties.Comments: The Rock Bluff fire started from a lightning storm that passed through earlier in the morning which also started the Marsh Unit 3 fire to the East. E-863 and several crews assisted in suppression efforts.

The Marsh Unit 3 fire started from a lightning storm, FWS, BLM and County Cooperators all responded in a unified effort to suppress. Trent Baker was an ICT4 trainee under Ryan Sharpe. Numerous aviation resources were also on scene
